title: Bug 109350- Output parameter not displayed in data set dialog
description: Output parameter not displayed in the data set dialog when querying from Oracle database.
OB: While in the query result page, no data is being returned. The expected behavior is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog.
SR:
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 
2. Check the query result page. 

Actual result: No data is being returned. 

Expected result: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
